**2.** If the annual interest rate is 12%, what will be the interest on Tk. 10,000 for 4 years?  
[NSI (Field Officer): 2021] + [Youth &amp; Sports Ministry: (Offi)-2025] + [C.A.AB-(Regular Officer):-2028]  
- a. Tk. 8900<br>  
- b. Tk. 8420<br>  
- c. Tk. 8680<br>  
- d. `Tk. 4800`<br>  

+++ Solution:  
I = (100 × 12 × 4) = 4800  
+++

